To add a class attribute to all h1 tags within a specific section, we can use the `querySelectorAll` method in JavaScript. We can also use the `classList` property to add the class attribute. Here's an example:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .section-h1 {
            color: red;
        }

        .section-h2 {
            color: blue;
        }
    </style>
